profile: Over 50 years of masonry excellence.  2nd generation family business.  Experts specializing in Chimney Removals and Repairs, Repointing, Brick and Stone Restoration and much more.  Quality Workmanship Guaranteed. Fully Insured for liability insurance and WSIB.  Two year workmanship warranty.  We provide residential repairs within the tri-cities and area.
services:
♦  Brick repair / Brick restoration
♦  Stone repair / Stone restoration
♦  Chimney repair / Chimney repointing
♦  Repointing brick and stone
♦  Cultured and natural stone installation
♦  Fireplace restoration
♦  Window and door sill repair
♦  Other new custom masonry jobs or masonry repairs
